<p id="Par26">Our statistical model is formulated as follows for Δ
 <italic>T</italic>; an identical and independent model is used for %Δ
 <italic>P</italic>. The estimate of future change in mean temperature between 
 <italic>t</italic> = 0 and 
 <italic>t</italic> = 1, 
 <italic>υ</italic>
 <sub>1</sub>, is based on historical observed temperature change to 
 <italic>t</italic> = 0, Δ
 <italic>X</italic>
 <sub>0</sub>:
 <disp-formula id="Equ1">
  <label>1</label>
